}.header{
	position:fixed;
	top:0;
	left:0;
	width:100%;
	color:#ddd;
	background:#fff;
	height:4rem;
	padding:0;
	z-index:200;
	box-shadow: 0 1px 0 #d6e0ea;
}
.header-div{
	display:flex;
	color:#fff;
	height:100%;
	align-items:center;
	position:relative;
	padding: 0 1rem;
}
.main-menu-toggle,
.menu-toggle {
	display: flex;
	align-items: center;
}
.main-menu-close,
.main-menu-open{
	stroke:#061726;
	stroke-width:2px;
	stroke-linecap: round;
	stroke-linejoin: round;
}
.main-menu-close{
	display:none;
	stroke-width:3px
}
.pop-show>.main-menu-close{display:inline-block}
.pop-show>.main-menu-open{display:none}
.header-logo{
	width:8rem;
	margin-right: 0.2rem;
	display: flex;
	flex-shrink:0;
	align-items: center;
}
.header-logo img {
	width: 100%;
	height: auto;
}
.header-upload{
	box-sizing: border-box;
	border-radius:10rem;
	padding: 0 0.35rem;
	height:2.6rem;
	width:2.6rem;
	margin:0 1rem 0 0.5rem;
	display: flex;
	align-items: center;
}
.header-upload svg {
	fill: #85C742;
	width: 100%;
}
.header-upload-menu {
	display: none;
	right: 0;
}
.header-upload-menu.pop-show {
	display: block;
}
main {
	display: block;
	margin-top: 4rem;
	overflow: hidden;
}
.u-deemphasized {
    color: #495a6a;
}

#main-menu.main-menu-nav-collapsed {
	box-shadow: none;
}
#main-menu.main-menu-nav-collapsed,
.main-menu-nav-collapsed .main-menu-heading {
	font-size: 10px;
	text-align: center;
}
.main-menu-nav-collapsed .main-menu-item-label,
.main-menu-item-label-collapsed {
	display: none;
}
.main-menu-nav-collapsed .main-menu-item-label-collapsed {
	display: block;
}
.main-menu-nav-collapsed .main-menu-item {
	display: flex;
	flex-direction: column;
	align-items: center;
}

.main-menu-nav-collapsed .main-menu-item {
	padding: 8px 5px;
}

.main-menu-nav-collapsed .main-menu-heading {
	padding: 1.5rem 5px 1rem;
}

.main-menu-nav-collapsed .main-menu-item-channel {
	padding: 4px 5px;
}
.main-menu-nav-collapsed .main-menu-icon,
.main-menu-nav-collapsed .user-image {
	flex-shrink: 0;
	width: 24px; height: 24px; font-size: 24px;
	margin-right: 0;
	margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
}
.main-menu-nav-collapsed .main-menu-icon {
	stroke-width: 1.5px;
}

.main-menu-nav-collapsed .main-menu-item-channel .user-image {
	flex-shrink: 0;
	width: 30px; height: 30px; font-size: 30px;
	margin: 0;
}.main-menu-toggle, .menu-toggle {
	padding: 1rem;
	margin-left: -1rem;
}
.header-search{
	display:flex;
	margin-left: auto;
	align-items:center;
	border-radius: 0.8rem;
}
.header-search-select, .header-search-field {
	border:0;
	height:100%;
	background-color:transparent;
	font-size:1.1rem;
	color:#000;
	outline-offset: 3px;
}
.header-search:focus-within {
	outline: 2px solid #0d2437;
}
.header-search-field:focus-visible,
.header-search-submit:focus-visible {
	outline: none;
}
.header-search-select {
    text-indent: 0.01px;
	width: 7rem;
	flex-shrink: 0;
	padding: 0 1.5rem 0 1rem;
	border:0;
}
.header-search-field{
	-webkit-appearance: textfield;
	width:100%;
	padding:0 0.7rem;
}
.header-search-field::-webkit-search-decoration {
	-webkit-appearance: none;
}
.header-search-field::placeholder{
	color:#061726;
}
.header-search-submit{
	height:2.5rem;
	width:2.5rem;
	padding:0.6rem;
	flex-shrink:0;
}
.header-search-select,.header-search-field{display:none;}
.header-search-select.pop-show,.header-search-field.pop-show{
	display:block;
}
.header-search.pop-show{
	position:absolute;
	left: 4rem;
	right: 1rem;
	z-index:100;
	background: white;
	border: 1px solid #D6E0EA;
}
.header-search-icon{
	stroke:#000;
	fill:#000;
}.header-user-info{display:none;}
.header-user{
	text-align:left;
}
i.header-user-img, svg.header-user-img {
	display: block;
	flex-shrink: 0;
	font-size: 2.6rem; width: 2.6rem; height: 2.6rem;
	padding:0.35rem;
}.navs{
	position:fixed;
	top:4rem;
	width:100%;
	z-index:10;
}
.hover-menu{
	position:absolute;
	background:#fff;
	width:16rem;
	padding: 0.5rem 0;
	box-sizing: border-box;
	box-shadow: 0 0 3rem 1rem rgba(6, 23, 38, 0.1);
	overflow: hidden auto;
	border: 1px solid #D6E0EA;
	border-radius: 0 0 5px 5px;
}
.hover-menu a {
	color: #1f2e3c;
}
.cxm {
	border-radius: 5px;
}
#main-menu{
	display:none;
	position:fixed;
	left: 0;
	top: 4rem;
	bottom: 0;
	background: #F3F5F8;
	width: 20rem;
	transition: width 200ms;
	border-radius: 0;
    font-size: 15px;
	padding-bottom: 3rem;
}
#main-menu.pop-show{
	display:block;
}
#main-menu.main-menu-nav-collapsed::-webkit-scrollbar {
	display: none;
}
#main-menu.main-menu-nav-collapsed {
	min-width: 0;
	width: 80px;
	-ms-overflow-style: none;
    scrollbar-width: none;
}.main-menu-item,
.cmi,
.cmx__section-head {
	display:block;
	padding: 8px 1rem;
	max-width: 100%;
	outline-offset: -3px;
}
a.main-menu-item {
	overflow: hidden;
	text-overflow: ellipsis;
	color: inherit;
}
a.main-menu-item-channel {
	display: flex;
	align-items: center;
	color: #1f2e3c;
	font-size: 13px;
	padding-top: 5px;
	padding-bottom: 5px;
	font-weight: 400;
}
.main-menu-item-channel .user-image {
	margin-right: 0.75rem;
}
.main-menu-item-channel-label {
    overflow: hidden;
    text-overflow: ellipsis;
    white-space: nowrap;
}
/* cxm = context menu */
.cxm {
	position: fixed;
	z-index: 210;
}
.cmx__section-head,
.main-menu-heading {
    color: #000;
	cursor: default;
	font-weight: 600;
}
.cmx__section-head {
}
/* cmi = context menu item */
.cmi {
	appearance: none;
	text-align: left;
	white-space: normal;
	width: 100%;
}
.cmi + .cmx__section-head {
	margin-top: 0.3rem;
	border-top: 1px solid #D6E0EA;
    padding-top: 0.7rem;
}
.main-menu-item-important{
	color: #D14900;
}
.main-menu-item:not(.main-menu-item--active):hover,
.cmi:not(.cmi--active):hover,
.cmi:not(.cmi--active):focus-visible {
	color: #1f2e3c;
	background-color: #8dd44728;
	text-decoration:none;
}
.cmi.cmi--info {
    color: #666;
    font-size: 1rem;
}
.cmi.cmi--info:hover {
    background: transparent;
    color: #666;
}
.main-menu-heading {
	border-top:1px solid #D6E0EA;
	padding: 1.2rem 1rem 0.8rem;
	margin: 0.9rem 0 0 0;
	position: relative;
}
.main-menu-heading-extra{
	position: absolute;
	bottom: 0.9rem;
	right: 1rem;
	font-size:12px;
	color: #495A6A;
}
:any-link > .main-menu-heading {
	cursor: pointer;
}
.main-menu-icon{
	width:1.428571429rem;
	height:1.428571429rem;
	margin-right: 0.5rem;
	position:relative;
	top: 0.3rem;
	stroke: #061726;
	stroke-width:2px;
	stroke-linejoin:round;
	stroke-linecap:round;
	fill:none;
}
.main-menu-item:hover:not(.main-menu-item--active) > .main-menu-icon {
	stroke: #386400;
	color: #386400;
}

.main-menu-item--active {
	background: #85C742;
	color: #fff;
	cursor: default;
}
a.main-menu-item--active {
	color: #fff;
}
.main-menu-item--active .main-menu-icon {
	stroke: currentColor;
}
.main-menu-item--active:hover {
	text-decoration: none;
}
.main-menu-signout {
	margin: 1rem 0 1.25rem;
}

.with-permanent-menu-expanded main {
	margin-left: 22rem;

		v=i.value.trim();

	e.preventDefault();
	if(!$$.isVisible(i)){
		$$.togglePopShow(e, [i,$$.getByClass('header-search')]);
	}else{
		if ( v == "" ) {
			i.focus();
			return false;
		}

		var submit_button = e.target;

		if(/^\/user\//g.test(location.pathname)){
			submit_button.setAttribute("disabled", "");
			location = location.pathname + "?q="+encodeURIComponent(v);
			return false;
		}

		submit_button.setAttribute("disabled", "");
		location = "/search/all?q="+encodeURIComponent(v);
	}
	return false;
});
